Hit SAVE to maximize your chest gainz! 💪💪💪
•
Incline Dumbbell Bench Press
•
1 warm up set (light weight, easily controlled throughout the entire set) 8 reps
4-5 working sets (progressively going up in weight each set by 10-15 pounds for each dumbbell until your final set is almost impossible) 6 reps
2-3 drop sets (as soon as you finish your final working set drop the weight 20-25%, count to 10 and then rep out to failure) shoot for minimum reps of 10-12, 15-16, and 18-20 for these drop sets
•
Try this technique for your entire workout and watch your chest grow exponentially 🔥🔥🔥
Don’t dream about success, work for it 🙏🌄
